cards.title: Purchase travel insurance
cards.description:
Given that cancellation risk starts immediately (usually, but check your policy). 
So consider purchasing your travel insurance as you decide on your travel 
dates and ideally before you start to purchase.

Important
Purchase your travel insurance policy when you start to make your first 
purchase!

Always read the fine print - the Policy Disclosure Statement (PDS)!
